## **Netwerk bouwen vanaf nul**

## **Configuratie R1**

**Basisconfiguratie**

hostname R1
enable secret cisco
line console 0
password console
login
logging synchronous
exit
service password-encryption

**Interfaces instellen**

interface GigabitEthernet0/0
description connection to SW1
 ip address 192.168.1.1 255.255.255.128
 ipv6 address 2001:db8:1::1/64
switchport mode trunk
switchport trunk allowed vlan 10,20
no shutdown
exit

interface GigabitEthernet0/1
description connection to SW2
ip address 192.168.1.129 255.255.255.128
ipv6 address 2001:db8:2::1/64
switchport mode trunk
switchport trunk allowed vlan 10,20
no shutdown
exit
ipv6 unicast-routing

**SSH instellen** 

ip domain-name netwerk.local
crypto key generate rsa modulus 2048
ip ssh version 2
username admin privilege 15 secret cisco
line vty 0 4
transport input ssh
login local
exit

## **Configuratie SW1** 

**Basisconfiguratie**

hostname SW1
enable secret cisco
line console 0
password console
login
exit
service password-encryption
banner motd #Authorized access only! #



**VLANâ€™s instellen**

vlan 10
name Sub1
exit

vlan 20
name Sub2
exit

interface Vlan10
ip address 192.168.1.2 255.255.255.128
ipv6 address 2001:db8:1::2/64
no shutdown
exit

interface Vlan20
ip address 192.168.1.130 255.255.255.128
ipv6 address 2001:db8:2::2/64
no shutdown
exit

ip default-gateway 192.168.1.1



**Poorten toewijzen**

interface GigabitEthernet0/1
 description connection to R1
 switchport mode trunk
 switchport trunk allowed vlan 10,20

interface GigabitEthernet0/2
description connection to SW2
 switchport mode trunk
 switchport trunk allowed vlan 10,20


interface range FastEthernet0/1-10
switchport mode access
switchport access vlan 10,20
exit

interface range FastEthernet0/11-20
switchport mode access
switchport access vlan 10,20
exit



**SSH Instellen**

ip domain-name netwerk.local
crypto key generate rsa modulus 2048
ip ssh version 2
username admin privilege 15 secret cisco

line vty 0 4
 transport input ssh
 login local

line console 0
 password console
 login




